cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

The paper deals with object detection and representation in videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model is a generative world model, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model also involves attention mechanisms and proposal-rejection mechanisms, which are commonly used in robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper discusses the scalability of the model, which is a common concern in neural networks (cs.NE).
